hat are the rules for the PVP Servers I Cant find a place to find this info out? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ucasieis.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Casieis</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/19/02 10:36:55 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: PVP Servers?</span><hr size=1> Broken. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ucasieis.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Casieis</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/19/02 10:40:01 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: PVP Servers?</span><hr size=1> Ok, so even though they're broken, here ya go:<br><br>Rallos Zek:  Free For All PVP, can hit anyone +/- 4 levels.  Loot 1 item and coin.  <br><br>Vallon/Tallon Zek:  Team based PvP (although you couldn't tell by the insanely sad state these servers are in), +/- 8 levels, loot coin.  Vallon has a player made LnS rule (loot and scoot), to leave the area for an hour after you dirtnap in PvP.  Very few follow this rule, however.  Mainly the top honorable guilds do, such as Defiant, Xanit K`Ven and Fated, but every guild has their moments. <br><br>Sullon Zek: This is the only PvP server I don't have a character above 50 on.  I'm not quite sure the rulset, although I know this for fact:  Training is legal, anyone can hit anyone, not sure how loot works although I think coin only for +/- 4 levels<br><br>-Casieis, <br>54th Rake<br>The Rathe<br><br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ukindelin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kindelin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/19/02 10:55:05 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: PVP Servers?</span><hr size=1> what ya mean there broken? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ucasieis.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Casieis</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/19/02 11:44:15 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: PVP Servers?</span><hr size=1> the state of Vallon and Tallon zek is really @#%$.  There are two teams, not the intended 4. Darkies and lighties, and a good 75% of the server is light based.  It really really sucks.  <br><br>When I go kill someone as Venric, my 54 darky warrior, I get pegged with 30 minutes worth of WHINE tells, &quot;YOU CHEAP PEICE OF CRAP&quot; &quot;YOU SUCK AT LIFE&quot; &quot;WTF WHY YOU KILL ME ALL I WANT IS XP&quot; &quot;OMG DONT HIT ME MY DOG IS DYING&quot; &quot;YOU WORTHLESS SACK OF (*&amp;(@#&amp;%(*&quot;... it's really lame.  If you don't wanna die to pvp, don't play pvp.  <br><br>The majority of the server never sees PvP until their 40's, 50's when they have no choice but to leave Lake of Ill Omen.  One guild pretty much dominates the server, Defiant.  Skill matters not when your opponent has 5-6 rightclickables, a 100k horse, primal weapons and the best TOV armor available to them.  Ever joust?  When I play on the rathe, the melee's I duel are sheep.  On Vallon, they're not.  But even still, I outmove my opponent almost ALWAYS, but no matter HOW much you can run circles around them, your hits for 40-50 per hack are really outmatched by his for 250-300.  <br><br>This is sounding like a major whine, but really, it's the reason I left Vallon.  The teams are so crazily unbalanced, its basically 3 teams vs 1.  A good number of players are of the lowest quality in all of Everquest.  I don't want to hear how your mother is sick and how your father beat you when I choose to kill you in Karnors castle.  It's a game.  I won.  Go away.<br><br>Very few battles end in &quot;nice fight&quot; or no talking at all, almost EVERYONE has a reason why you sent them to their bindspot.  I go out to PvP almost all the time I'm on the server, and I see new level 60's popping up every day.  These are referred to as Velketor noobs.  Ever see a monk with a tranquil staff, fungi tunic, insane cloak haste, full blue diamond jewellery, level 60 with 3 AA points in speed get completely destroyed by someone 6 levels below them?  This is why Vallon is horrible.  People don't pvp.  They don't play the server for what it is.  If an Elf kills a human, even if that humans a shadowknight for crying outloud, they're blacklisted as PKer's.  What the hell man? it's a PvP server!  /sigh<br><br>I'm sooo ranting here, so I'm going to end it<br><br>-Casieis, <br>54th Rake<br>The Rathe<br><br>-Venric Nar`Kelaz<br>54th Champion<br>Vallon Zek<br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uglipthegnome.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Glip the Gnome</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Pantsless Asst. Administrator</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/19/02 11:56:18 pm)</font><br>     <br>Community Supporter<br> <BR><img src=http://www.keithparkinson.com/glip2.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: PVP Servers?</span><hr size=1> Your original thread was moved to our PvP forum.  Please continue discussions <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showMessage?topicID=626.topic>here</a> <